is an excellent resource for expert speakers on numerous topics, including issues in the healthcare industry, medical education, diseases, and biomedical and clinical research. Recognized on an international scale, our dedicated faculty and physicians may be available to speak at your organization, at schools and at media events. For more information on how to obtain a speaker for your next event, please call at (815) 395-5601 or [email protected] . About  Education  Research  Patient Care  Departments  News  Giving INFORMATION FOR: Prospective and Current Students  Faculty & Staff  Alumni & Friends  Patients  Businesses and Community RESOURCES: UIC Directory  Blackboard  Emergency Information  Contact Us  Apply Now  Give  Contact Us Connect with us!    If you have questions, comments, or problems accessing this site, please E-mail the webmaster  © Copyright 2019 University of Illinois College of Medicine   | Privacy Statement College of Medicine | Chicago | Peoria | Rockford | Urbana                                                                                                                                             